{"tid":1447630,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】盧偉聰醫院探燒傷警員","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:05:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T04:22:54.000Z","uid":66271,"like":14,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"d7f30ef01fffcddfec79c32cce1403ecb52fa13e","tid":1447630,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:05:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190811/s00001/0b3dde77eeb27227fdfab33ecd782d27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190811%2Fs00001%2F0b3dde77eeb27227fdfab33ecd782d27.jpg&h=54db61e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方發稿，表示警務處長盧偉聰今晚（11日）到瑪嘉烈醫院探望今日較早前，在尖沙嘴警署內執勤時被「暴徒」投擲汽油彈引致雙腳燒傷的一名警員。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰表示，對暴徒罔顧他人安全的非法暴力行為感到非常憤慨，予以最強烈譴責。他稱，針對任何引致他人身體嚴重受傷、甚至威脅生命安全的暴力行為，警隊必定全力追究。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你警察就係人，咁個女仔呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"ab5c8ac9f6c70acb2aa954ff31536741bcd36fe3","tid":1447630,"uid":16676,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:06:24.000Z","msg":"前線大量鬼<br />\n大量臥底扮手足<br />\n著到十足十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />葵芳<span style=\"color: green;\">果粒煙花</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Full Gear 豬嘴有耳機,有對講機 小心</strong></span></span><br />\n黑警扮示威者<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">CWB 有人點火, 汽油彈, 掉磚頭, 燒垃圾筒</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警已經與恐怖組織無異</span></strong></span><br />\n佢地已經潛伏前線<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />當日有份助攻衝立法會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係點解唔成立調查委員會原因"},{"pid":"5b3cc86875f1adf7fe570e79c559d463fd8a5586","tid":1447630,